src:
Winning numbers drawn in 'Numbers Evening' game
04 Nov 2019, 00:10 by The Associated Press
CRANSTON, R.I. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Sunday evening's drawing of the Rhode Island Lottery's "Numbers Evening" game were:
5-6-7-0
(five, six, seven, zero)
